channel.title: Solved! Lock Please
channel.description: I Cant Publish My Server Because Whenever I Open My Client, My Name And Password Comes Up, I Made A Different Account And Logged Into That And Then Reset The Client But The First One Came Up Again. What Shall i Do?

item.title: Solved! Lock Please
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Brandon12111 Mod Brandon12111
item.description:
@Mod_Brandon12111 wrote:

This goes 1 of two ways, #1 either you have something in server-side or client-side that’s keeping it there as in it saves ur username and password (like a website for example) so just find where it is and take it off. #2 If this is not the case, I’d try looking at your Sprites, etc to see if you’re missing a loginbox or create a new one to see if that gets rid of it.
